{"tid":981890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬道立：司法人員宣誓時應奏唱國歌","createTime":"2019-01-14T15:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T11:00:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ff68825b11edb511c93ef1db18f5da9728e5c81b","tid":981890,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20140113-Legal-Year-5-s20copy_MPOeA_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20140113-Legal-Year-5-s20copy_MPOeA_1200x0.jpg&h=d4c1475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438035-20190114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438035-20190114.htm&d=Kj2VNr%2Fz%2FzEZPka8Htooby7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=676ce386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438035-20190114.htm&h=502593a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438035-20190114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n終審法院首席法官馬道立出席法律年度開啟典禮後表示，司法人員宣誓時應該奏唱國歌。他說儀式重要，奏唱國歌可以顯示司法人員對香港法治的承擔，正如法律年度開啟典禮前亦會播放。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立又期望，市民了解司法制度及個別案件的判詞，才作評論，並期望市民對本港司法制度有信心。<br />\n<br />\n對於提出與律政司商討修訂法例，提高處理免遣返聲請的效率，馬道立說，涉及免遣返聲請的司法覆核，由2016年的60宗增至去年3000宗，有關修訂只屬程序修訂，旨在提升效率。"},{"pid":"5c1679fe766f465ac62d83bccb37c9ca387657ad","tid":981890,"uid":216441,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"奶鞋底奶到咁出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281561c54c443256ad98b5997fb978cb89552f99","tid":981890,"uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"外籍法官要用蝗語唱支那匪歌？<br />\n<br />\nCLS"},{"pid":"c9eeb083abff102eb00cd7734a7a7d578a70b90b","tid":981890,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:51:1