eabb63854ecf066bb2b31a09aeeeb2","tid":981890,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20140113-Legal-Year-5-s20copy_MPOeA_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20140113-Legal-Year-5-s20copy_MPOeA_1200x0.jpg&h=d4c1475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438035-20190114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438035-20190114.htm&d=Kj2VNr%2Fz%2FzEZPka8Htooby7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=676ce386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438035-20190114.htm&h=502593a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438035-20190114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n終審法院首席法官馬道立出席法律年度開啟典禮後表示，司法人員宣誓時應該奏唱國歌。他說儀式重要，奏唱國歌可以顯示司法人員對香港法治的承擔，正如法律年度開啟典禮前亦會播放。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立又期望，市民了解<span style=\"color: red;\">司法制度及個別案件的判詞</span>，才作評論，並期望市民對本港司法制度有信心。<br />\n<br />\n對於提出與律政司商討修訂法例，提高處理免遣返聲請的效率，馬道立說，涉及免遣返聲請的司法覆核，由2016年的60宗增至去年3000宗，有關修訂只屬程序修訂，旨在提升效率。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n誰大誰惡誰最正確<br />\n人大話你犯法就係犯法 人大話你冇犯法就冇 呢個未香港的司法制度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇嚟要讀多D書"},{"pid":"a096ac84ee8dfcff58097bcae6e062cbfa37dca8","tid":981890,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f68a4e9c389932c7743d831623290889ea2cf3a","tid":981890,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ba72fecfa6e910558ebce797652d8b8c419ca22","tid":981890,"uid":5489,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a53fb0c6d908be44054b72f984f9909db59a3b7","tid":981890,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪唔好黎香港從事法律事業<br />\n黎到香港，就入鄉隨俗，基本禮貌啦下話"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"7